Belka Says ‘Somebody Will Definitely Lose Money’ on Betting Against Zloty

-- B y   N a t h a n i e l   E s p i n o
-- 
2011-09-09T11:23:45Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-09/belka-says-somebody-will-definitely-lose-money-on-betting-against-zloty.html
“Somebody will definitely lose
money” betting against the Polish zloty, central bank Governor
Marek Belka said in an interview with TVN CNBC television today,
saying the central bank wouldn’t react to investors’ attempts to
“provoke” the Narodowy Bank Polski to intervene on the market.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Nathaniel Espino at 
 nespino@bloomberg.net  